{"tid":130100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國出生大熊貓「寶寶」返中國　6萬人往動物園道別","createTime":"2017-02-22T06:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T17:26:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dedba619078d7cf5536e1eb8fd848c8b16ae9bd1","tid":130100,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170222/s00005/1487743656285SL4_7BFDF3F5764CA41588A33A3F5C2CB5BB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170222%2Fs00005%2F1487743656285SL4_7BFDF3F5764CA41588A33A3F5C2CB5BB.jpg&h=f5fcc76c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在美國出生的大熊貓「寶寶」啟程返回中國，牠會從華盛頓乘搭16小時直航航班到成都。<br />\n<br />\n「寶寶」在當地時間周二（21日）離開華盛頓國家動物園，由兩名動物員的工作人員陪同，乘搭16小時直航機前往成都，工作人員為牠準備重約30公斤的食物，當中主要是竹子，但亦有蘋果、番薯等。「寶寶」抵達成都後，會先接受一個月隔離，之後會加入大熊貓保育計劃的基地。<br />\n<br />\n3歲半的雌性大熊貓「寶寶」2013年8月在華盛頓國家動物園出生，父母分別為19歲的「添添」和18歲的「美香」，牠們與「寶寶」的1歲弟弟「貝貝」仍留在該動物園。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國和中國的協議，在中國以外出生的大熊貓，須在滿4歲前返回中國。「寶寶」離開美國前的最後一個周末，有約6萬人前往動物園與牠道別。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社/華盛頓郵報）<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170222/s00005/1487743712772#sthash.eZk6HuT1.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170222%2Fs00005%2F1487743712772%23sthash.eZk6HuT1.dpuf&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=7d189fb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170222%2Fs00005%2F1487743712772%23sthash.eZk6HuT1.dpuf&h=1215b609\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170222/s00005/1487743712772#sthash.eZk6HuT1.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"c6c1af7b0bfd68259dadf152f7396c9ed66453fa","tid":130100,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"返中國會唔會毒撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc75d0